com.example.trialio.controllers

Class TrialManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.trialio.controllers.TrialManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TrialManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    TrialManager manages Trials for an experiment and is responsible for the persistence of Trial data. This class is used to perform create, read, update and delete functionality on experiment trials that are uploaded for an experiment. This class communicates with the Firebase database.
